# 🍽️ Recipes Web Project

## 🚀 Project Description
A beginner-friendly HTML project that showcases multiple food recipes.  
Each recipe includes ingredients, preparation steps, and images.

## 🎯 Objectives
- Practice HTML fundamentals
- Learn how to structure a multi-page project
- Understand linking between pages
- Apply proper folder organization

## 🛠 Features
- Homepage with recipe list
- Individual recipe pages
- Images for each recipe
- Clean and simple layout

## 📚 Lessons Learned
I learned how to properly link pages using relative paths and improved my understanding of HTML document structure.